title.rendered: 5 Pack, BSN Medical Propax Combine Dressings 9cm x 20cm Sterile Non-Woven Wound Dressing

content.rendered: The pack consists of absorbent pads that are non-woven and rayon perforated. The pads are designed to be flat, have open ends and are to be used only when sterile. They can be used either directly for heavy leaking wounds or a secondary dressing.
